<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scufundari</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
        .image-end-1{
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 340px;
            width: 380px;
            margin: 40px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #aaaaaa;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://www.tripsavvy.com/thmb/AIiNbdjY4ZXYKIDPdoRe9f1MclA=/2121x1193/smart/filters:no_upscale()/egypt--red-sea--hurghada--young-woman-snorkeling-at-coral-reef-926722356-5269429ca25a49d8877b57ab4a249856.jpg");
        }
        .dark{
            background-color: #333;
        }
        .image-end-1-big{
            z-index: 111;
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 540px;
            width: 880px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 400px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://www.tripsavvy.com/thmb/AIiNbdjY4ZXYKIDPdoRe9f1MclA=/2121x1193/smart/filters:no_upscale()/egypt--red-sea--hurghada--young-woman-snorkeling-at-coral-reef-926722356-5269429ca25a49d8877b57ab4a249856.jpg");
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 15px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgb(37, 37, 37); 
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #333; 
            border-radius: 25px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #555; 
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div id="image-1-big" class="image-end-1-big invisible"></div>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Scufundari</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Scufundari (2 plimbari) ,relaxare pe vas ,pranz pe vas, bauturi non alcoolice, pretul include asigurarea obligatorie pentru diving
        . Plecarea  va fi in jurul orei 08: 00 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati iar sosirea in jurul orei 18 : 00 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati si de trafic.
        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        Adult : 25 €<br>
        Copil : 15 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        in fiecare zi
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Diving (2 walks), relaxation on the boat, lunch on the boat, non-alcoholic drinks, the price includes compulsory insurance for diving
        . Departure will be around 08:00 depending on the hotel where you are staying and arrival around 18:00 depending on the hotel where you are staying and traffic.        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        Adult: 25 €<br>
        Children: 15 €
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        every day
    </p>
    <div class="images-section" id="images-section">
        <div id="image-1" class="image-end-1"></div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    const image1 = document.getElementById("image-1")
    const imageBig1 = document.getElementById("image-1-big")
    const body = document.querySelector("body")

    image1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.remove("invisible")
        body.classList.add("dark")
        image1.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    imageBig1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.add("invisible")
        body.classList.remove("dark")
        image1.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>